summary: This appears to be a law enforcement log entry from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) dated August 10, 2019, the day Jeffrey Epstein was found dead in his cell. events.title: Jeffrey Epstein's death in custody
events.description: Jeffrey Epstein was found dead in his cell at the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York. The document is a lieutenant's log and daily activity report from that date, likely documenting the incident and related activities.

keyFacts: The document is a lieutenant's log and daily activity report from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) dated August 10, 2019.
